# Final Report

## Project Title
Fake News Detection using Deep Learning

## Problem
Classify news articles as fake or real.

## Dataset
Fake and Real News Dataset (Kaggle)

## Preprocessing
- Removed missing values  
- Cleaned text  
- Tokenized and padded sequences  

## Models
- Baseline: Logistic Regression (TF-IDF)  
- Deep Learning: LSTM  

## Results
| Model | Accuracy | F1-score |
|------|--------|---------|
| Logistic Regression | 0.95 | 0.95 |
| LSTM | 0.97 | 0.97 |

## Error Analysis
Model struggles with long and ambiguous texts.

## Conclusion
Deep learning improved performance over baseline.

